Challenge tens of thousands of real players at the World Cup, Crazy Days and during the seasons of the Crazy 8 Pro League to become the best of all and grab the Jackpot!

PLAY MULTIPLAYER (WITH FRIENDS OR AGAINST OTHER PLAYERS)
- Play against other players online;
- Organize private games with friends or work out against Kooko;
